::Diamond::
She walked in and looked at Megatron and KiKat."I am here to talk to 
the leader of this group. Which one of you is KitKat?"

::KitKat::
She looked at Diamond. "I am KitKat. What is it that I can do for 
you?"

Diamond::
"Forgive me," she bowed. "I see that you are busy. I wish to talk to 
you when you get the chance."

::KitKat::
"I shall see you as soon as I am done here. Please wait just outside 
and we'll talk in a bit."

Diamond::
She smiled. "I thank you." She turned and walked out of the room. She 
waited just outside the room.
